{"tid":1623012,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［長期抗爭］全民無限期生病正式開始","createTime":"2019-10-04T17:57:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T06:30:44.000Z","uid":199769,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"563cc0cdeacc08ea4fd0aa24ed189b25d1f6f397","tid":1623012,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:57:53.000Z","msg":"問：推咗禁蒙面法啦，送頭坐一年監？<br />\n答：睇返條例，禁蒙面情況限於集會及非法集會。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">日常生活下，生病帶口罩不在限制範圍內</span></span>。</strong> 最多<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">被狗逗下，要除罩。記得要配合除，咁先長玩長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zu7Ssf6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZu7Ssf6.png&h=8a8c9ab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ExtinVw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FExtinVw.png&h=69e80c33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成效：<br />\n1. 空氣質素差，出街又好，返工都好，大家平時要帶下口罩。全民口罩，正是抗拒極權惡法嘅有力展現。<br />\n<br />\n2. 避免一啲長期需要帶口罩嘅手足被狗咬。<br />\n<br />\n風險：<br />\n問：屌，現加啲狗咁惡，亂咬人，咪以為佢會跟規矩啦。<br />\n答：自行衡量風險，真係好驚被狗咬傷嘅，帶口罩時避免接近集會現場。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果不幸附近冇集會，行行下街都被狗咬，一來又有大把料文宣，二來藍絲朋友他朝君體也相同，班中立港豬又增加無辜受牽連的機會，國際戰線又見識到港共政府力量。攬炒路線又行前一大步。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">總結：<br />\n大家有咩唔舒服記得帶口罩。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"dc65426ce80b42fb52c3da13c90905966e2f824a","tid":1623012,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:58:11.000Z","msg":"自推10下"},{"pid":"ca4e04353df69ec45760791cb98d8413e36f0a96","tid":1623012,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:58:29.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"22a9023097aa969e46693fc857371b30d847a422","tid":1623012,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:58:33.000Z","msg":"［極重要］做嘢還做嘢，P牌仔想畀個革命方向大家討論討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1621742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1621742</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c3630b773e10c4c3a17c442201ce7f395094ccfd","tid":1623012,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:59:09.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"1d38afb1bd892786cff82984b1fb525b808cd535","tid":1623012,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:59:32.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"d164ca7041a8a5970a692e08f4e2e05867afe1d8","tid":1623012,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:59:42.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"5ffaf596de59ce10e08de1d28d68ab3e67de197d","tid":1623012,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:00:01.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"0973559e19131d5a9ef5de1c4794af3b2f6121d6","tid":1623012,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:00:15.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"1dd40e266a5a46038b3814e050315dbdf1008fc6","tid":1623012,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:01:20.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"8f8f0eb8e6e4a85e594bc96d564b178a404f0b76","tid":1623012,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:01:30.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"abce5698b9e81e15191d9affbba53cc076beec7d","tid":1623012,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:03:13.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"e0f089329a3e3372b0246d1af11397736c92f975","tid":1623012,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:03:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">破解緊急法！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">只有全民<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無&middot;限&middot;期</span>罷工罷課先可以救自己、救香港！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610341</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">早前政府宣布，香港各區發生暴動！今日宣布立緊急法</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">亦即係話，當日只要出過街嘅非警察人士，都有機會告你參與暴動</span>！<span style=\"color: red;\">要去狗屋坐48個鐘，而且定罪嘅話一坐就幾年</span>！<br />\n<br />\n打工反學嘅你，為你自己將來，呼籲大家，<span style=\"color: red;\">盡快組織無限期罷工、罷課</span>！<span style=\"color: gold;\">只有咁，先可以癱瘓社會運作，直到政府宣布徹底妥協為止！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n罷工，你可能面對被炒魷魚嘅風險，但罷工不需要附上刑責！警察唔可能上門捉你返工！<span style=\"color: red;\">只要齊心，換來嘅係政府徹底讓步！大家包括今日有出街嘅人亦唔會被告暴動！警察亦可以立即停止暴力，義士亦可以沉冤得雪</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">如果大家唔齊心罷工，有一日警察會上門捉你，告你暴動！就算唔係，警察以後亦會變本加厲，用更重手對付大家！以後大家無機會出聲！</span>今日見到已經開槍謀殺義士！我地一定要立即制止納粹警暴歪風！請大家立即籌備無限期罷工、罷課！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>請文宣幫手將以上論點製作poster廣傳，多謝各位</strong>"},{"pid":"fc99600d8288b4ecb19cf0c300755cf30f822ffe","tid":1623012,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:03:53.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"a6f5a6a06f7cab50f1df0b6f8d96e598ec43d54c","tid":1623012,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:04:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"500e3915089941c10124db285dfa2898050ae79c","tid":1623012,"uid":279994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:04:58.000Z","msg":"周街山埃 唔戴口罩點呼吸<br />\n同香港邊個冇鼻敏感咖?!"},{"pid":"912bc090c09242039a689dd064ebc330e0077f5c","tid":1623012,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:05:03.000Z","msg":"真心有得搞"},{"pid":"66af5678aafbd56a9d0965bfd9f296fae15c3497","tid":1623012,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:05:29.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"20f18c1054582d03119d95f65327286f356a87d2","tid":1623012,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:06:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6da353861b18746644a4ee3b3606cd4ea5e393d1","tid":1623012,"uid":199769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04